{
  "texts": [
    "Note that, for now, we are using \"agent\" in line with the way this notion is used in AI and robotics, as a system receiving inputs and acting upon the environment (Russell and Norvig 2021, Ch.",
    "2; see also Floridi and Sanders 2004).",
    "We will further explore the agency of affective artificial agents in §4.",
    "Affective artificial agents are nothing new, at least from a conceptual point of view.",
    "Artificial systems affectively interacting with humans have increasingly been a recurrent motif in 20-th century science fiction, and the trend seems nowhere near an end."
  ]
}